```plantuml
@startuml de1ux_statlord

actor User as U
participant "Dashboard Editor" as DE
participant "API" as API
participant "Display Management" as DM
participant "Display Rendering" as DR

U -> DE: Open Dashboard Editor
DE -> API: Fetch Layouts
API -> DE: Return Layouts

U -> DE: Create/Modify Layout
DE -> API: Save Layout
API -> DE: Confirm Save

U -> DM: Register Display
DM -> API: Save Display Configuration
API -> DM: Confirm Save

U -> DE: Assign Layout to Display
DE -> DM: Assign Layout
DM -> API: Update Display Layout
API -> DM: Confirm Update

DE -> API: Fetch Data
API -> DE: Return Data

DE -> DR: Render Dashboard
DR -> Display: Display Data

@enduml
```